    public class HeatmapMenu
extends javax.swing.JFrame

    A JFrame menu that displays a heatmap and presents controls that can change the appearance and backing data for the heatmap.

        private boolean distanceChanged
        States whether the distance has been changed. If this is true while criteriaChanged is false, then the heatmap should be regenerated (distances SHOULD NOT be recalculated).
